Starscream looked at Megatron, who appeared busy with other things. 
Than a familiar bot came in: Waspinator. A smirk came on Waspinators 
face. Waspinator couldn't have reckognixed him in this body. He just 
laughed inside and continued.

"Please Megatron, let me join you!"
